page.title: 03LIFE IN LETWELL
page.content: On{Tuesday 2nd}of{July}breakfast was tinned pineapple and pineapple juice. After that I walked upstairs and cleaned my teeth. I then carried my heavy bags up the road to catch the school bus. It soon came and took me to school in{Woodsetts }where I would hope to get a good days work done but that was before I had remembered that we were having {Assembly. Assembly today is where people go to tell everybody something special. School soon ended after a fairly good days work mostly copying up and soon I was boarding the school bus. I arrived { {home}about{4.00pm}to a{Italian}meal of spaghetti bolognaise because Ihad only had sandwiches for lunch. I watched {television}as my mum drove off to { {Tesco}(a big supermarket). Before I went to bed I had a drink of{milk }and a {Kit Kat.}But soon I went to bed.
